TRUST RELATIONSHIP
=> Relationship b/w two domains.
=> Trouble shooting in Trust Relationship.
6 types of Trust : 
  => Tree-Root Trust
  => Parent-Child Trust
  => Shortcut Trust
  => External Trust
  => Forest Trust
  => Realm Trust
