USER ACCOUNT AND GROUPS
* Users
* Groups
* Kali cmds : 
    => users
    => groups
    => cat /etc/passwd
    => sudo useradd user1
    => getnet passwd
    => sudo useradd user2
    => getnet passwd
    => sudo useradd user3
    => getnet passwd
* resetting the password : sudo passwd user1
* open a new group : sudo groupadd group
    => group1
    => group2
    => group3
*  to delete a group : sudo delgroup group1
